                  <br />

                   Date:
                  </strong>
                  <br />
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Thursday, January 12, 2017

                  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;
                  <br />

                  <br />
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 6 &ndash; 8:30 p.m.

                  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;
                  <br />

                  <strong>
                   Location:
                  </strong>
                  <br />
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; M. J. O'Connor's Irish Pub - Back Bay
                  <br />
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Park Plaza
                  <br />
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 27 Columbus Ave.
                  <br />
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Boston, Mass.&nbsp; 02116

                  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;
                  <br />
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
                  <a href="http://www.mjoconnors.com/" target="_blank" title="M. J. O'Connors Irish Pub">

                  </a>
                  <br />
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;
                  <br />

                  <strong>

                  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; New England Regional Alumni Club

                  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;
                  <br />
                  <strong>

                  <br />
